  <div class="rte">
    <h2>Shipping Policy</h2>
    <p>
      We provide shipping services to locations around the world. Enjoy free standard shipping on orders over US$350.
      Expedited shipping is available as a paid option.
    </p>

    <h3>Order Processing</h3>
    <p>Orders are usually processed within 1-3 business days during standard operating hours and workdays.</p>
    <p>If an item is out of stock or on pre-order, we will reach out to you directly.</p>
    <p>During sale periods, please allow an additional 1-2 days for order processing.</p>

    <h3>Delivery Times</h3>
    <p>
      Standard shipping typically requires 7-15 business days, while expedited shipping generally takes 2-12 business
      days.
    </p>
    <p>Delivery times may vary by region.</p>
    <p>
      Please note that delivery times can be affected by factors such as customs processes or unexpected environmental
      conditions.
    </p>
    <p>
      For specific delivery time requirements, please contact our customer service team at
      <a href="mailto:tsuki_official@qq.com">tsuki_official@qq.com</a> for tailored assistance.
    </p>

    <h3>Customs & Duties</h3>
    <p>
      Please be advised that the quoted prices exclude any applicable customs duties, import taxes, or related fees.
    </p>
    <p>
      The recipient is responsible for the payment of all such charges levied by the customs authorities of the
      destination country.
    </p>
    <p>
      Shipments will be held by customs or the designated carrier until all applicable fees have been paid and processed
      prior to release for delivery.
    </p>

    <h2>Return Policy</h2>
    <p>We accept returns under the following conditions:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Items damaged during shipping</li>
      <li>Items with quality issues</li>
      <li>Wrong items were shipped</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Size Exchange</h3>
    <p>
      Exchanges for different sizes are allowed only if the item is in stock. If the requested size is sold out or
      available for pre-order, exchange cannot be processed.
    </p>
    <p>Customers are responsible for all shipping expenses related to exchanges, including:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Return shipping of original item</li>
      <li>Delivery of replacement item</li>
      <li>Any applicable customs duties</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Size Exchange Conditions:</h4>
    <ul>
      <li>Original item must be returned in good condition with original packaging</li>
      <li>Item label must remain intact. Removal will disqualify the item from exchange</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Order Cancellation</h3>
    <p>Orders can be cancelled before shipment. Once shipped, cancellation is not possible.</p>
  </div>
</div>
